VERSION 1
WHEN PRESENT \bstd::ofstream\s*\(
WHEN EXPR MISSING:umask|S_IRUSR|S_IWUSR|0600|0640|0644
REPORT AS area_of_interest
REASON Detects the use of `std::ofstream` for file creation without specifying secure permissions.
TRACE Externalized rule logic for Unsafe File Creation with Incorrect Permissions.
